== Research Interests
- Network telemetry (网络测量)
  -- Sketch, eBPF, In-network measurement
- Advanced data structures and indexes (概率性数据结构、随机性数据结构、学习型索引)
  -- Filter, Learned Indexes, Hash Table
- AI for DB
  -- Key-value store
  -- Approximate Query Processing

~~~
